# Proto Admin Portal (this repo)

This is the **only** codebase for https://protoportal-admin.vercel.app.

## Separation from main portal

| | Admin (this repo) | Main portal |
|--|-------------------|-------------|
| Repo | `danieljoffeinfo-web/protoportal-admin` | `danieljoffeinfo-web/Proto-Website-` (protoportal-main) |
| URL | protoportal-admin.vercel.app | protoportal-main.vercel.app |

Never merge admin back into the main repo. Never reference or restore the old embedded admin in protoportal-main.

## Auth

**No login/authentication yet.** `Root.jsx` uses a temporary hardcoded admin customer. Do not assume Supabase auth, sessions, or role checks exist.

## Before any change

1. `git pull origin main` (or current branch)
2. Confirm which sections/APIs exist in the current `AdminPage.jsx` — this app has more modules than the deprecated embedded version (New Products, WhatsApp, Banner, Analytics, etc.)
3. Push to **this** repo; Vercel project is `protoportal-admin` only

## Key paths

- `src/pages/AdminPage.jsx` — all admin sections
- `src/components/ReorderGrid.jsx` — reorder grid UI
- `src/lib/products.js`, `src/lib/taxonomyAdmin.js` — catalogue data
- `api/` — serverless endpoints (image processing, WhatsApp, taxonomy, etc.)

Read `.cursor/skills/protoportal-admin/SKILL.md` for full architecture.
